headline: Williams-Sonoma, Inc. declares quarterly cash dividend
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, June 12, 2025--Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.66 per share of common stock. Each stockholder of record as of the close of business on July 18, 2025 will be paid the cash dividend on August 22, 2025.
